We have to be all, we must all catch up with being extremely fortunate. 

28
00:03:27,170 --> 00:03:34,412
The Quran describes "the Elite of the Elite" or the extremely fortunate ones, are those who are close to Us. 

29
00:03:34,412 --> 00:03:40,960
When you walk in this mosque and you get this message first-hand, 

30
00:03:40,960 --> 00:03:44,873
there's a great responsibility that goes with it. 

31
00:03:44,873 --> 00:03:55,362
When you walk through this door, you are applying for the highest position in the Hereafter for eternity. 

32
