He said that. We have to believe that. 

76
00:07:38,638 --> 00:07:46,394
In Sura 33, verse 40, and in 33:7

77
00:07:46,394 --> 00:07:50,911
In 3:81, God said that after all the prophets, God will send a messenger. 

78
00:07:50,911 --> 00:07:53,223
We have to believe that. 

79
